



if single statement is there inside if else do we need braces??



Q1: Valid
	if(true)
		System.out.println("Hello");
	
Q2: Not Valid 
	if(true)
		int x = 10;
	
	Note :  Curly braces are optional and without curly braces we can take only one statement which
	 should not be declerative statement.
	 
Q3:
	if(true);

	 